findings.title: Unused code present in the codebase
findings.description: There are a few instances of unused code (dead code) in the codebase, that is suggested to be removed.

findings.title: Reversed order of parameters in allowance function call
findings.description: When trying to pull the maximum amount of tokens from an approver to the allowed spender, the parameters used for the allowance function call are not in the same order as is used later in the call to safeTransferFrom.
